Tips for AND:
- Use AND when every condition must be true.
- Add parentheses when combining AND with OR.
- Use AND with text, numeric, pattern, and range filters.
- AND works in SELECT, UPDATE, DELETE, and other SQL statements.

Use this file as a complete reference for the SQL AND operator and many examples.
